{"title":"My 1st card Trick","date":"2023-08-27T03:30:30.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Aug 27, 2023","L":"08/27/2023","MM-DD":"08-27"},"link":"2023/08/27/My-1st-card-Trick","tags":["card trick"],"updated":"2023-08-31T10:24:30.674Z","content":"<p>welcome to my 1st post of card trick,and my github account is <a href=\"https://github.com/fightagainstdev?tab=repositories/\" target=\"_blank\">Here</a></p>\n<p>接下来向您展示的是我将用到的七副牌（象征着1周中的7天）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/08/30/pPdywZt.jpg\" alt=\"全部来自bicycle\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>####整副牌从上至下，从左至右依次是</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>-黑色常规 奥德赛 催眠 建筑奇迹<br>\n-暗号!(最贵的) 海王 狮子座<br>\n<em><strong>这个魔术被称为 CHICAGO OPENER</strong></em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"用到的手法：-double-lift\">用到的手法： <a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/103554597\">double lift</a><a title=\"#用到的手法：-double-lift\" href=\"#用到的手法：-double-lift\"></a></h3>\n<p><font color='' size=4 face='楷体'>首先我们让观众抽一张牌，之后让观众记住对应牌的点数与花色，我们将牌一张张或多张发下，让观众随意喊停并在停的位置盖上所有牌。接着一打响指后，整副牌就会多出一张与其他牌颜色不同的牌（1层效果）且此牌为观众的牌。将此牌放在一边。再重复前述步骤，发现放在一边的牌变成了第二张牌。</p>\n<blockquote><p>Just do it, anything is possible.</p>\n<footer><strong>slogan</strong><cite>from Nike</cite></footer></blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">alert(&#x27;welcome to magic world!&#x27;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"the 2nd 一些控顶手法","link":"2023/08/31/the-2nd-一些控顶手法"},"plink":"https://space.bilibili.com/588129/2023/08/27/My-1st-card-Trick/","toc":[{"id":"用到的手法：-double-lift","title":"用到的手法： double lift","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"245 words in 2 min"}